data.description: A stunning three-bedroom home nestled in The Ranch at Long Mountain subdivision. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by the Flagstone rock detailing and iron screen door. Inside, you'll be impressed by all the natural light created by the vaulted ceilings and Plantation Shutters. The living room features a gas log fireplace and pot shelves. The kitchen has Corian countertops, a farmhouse sink, tiled backsplash, and hardwood cabinets. On the exterior, you'll find a fully landscaped yard with fruit trees, a covered patio, shade screens, and a 10x12 shed with a loft. The attached garage offers three spaces for extra storage or all your toys, and there is also a 10x50 concrete slab for RV parking with 30amp hookups.
